OL,7,FEuropean politicians have criticised
OL,8,Fthe plan unveiled by Home Secretary
OL,9,FSuella Braverman on Tuesday to stop
OL,10,F"small boats" crossing the Channel,
OL,11,Fquestioning whether it would breach
OL,12,Finternational law and whether it would
OL,13,Fwork in practice.
OL,15,FThe legislation aims to ban those
OL,16,Farriving in the UK in the vessels from
OL,17,Fclaiming asylum in the country at all
OL,18,Fand will compel the Government to
OL,19,Fdetain and then deport them to their
OL,20,Fhome country or a safe third country.
